{"tid":776985,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推石內卜","createTime":"2018-08-12T14:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T22:47:42.000Z","uid":194101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f2e095a304d17dc3c6f1e337a777e4dd5df207","tid":776985,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"暢銷小說改編電影《哈利波特》系列大受歡迎，首集《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》原來已經是2001年上映，陪伴許多8、90後一同成長，戲中飾演「石內卜教授」教授的英國男星Alan Rickman因胰臟癌去世，令不少戲迷都相當傷心。一批Alan Rickman生前的私人信件近日被公開作慈善拍賣而曝光，其中一封更提到原來他曾經因「石內卜」一角感到非常挫敗，令戲迷都非常痛心。<br />\n<br />\n在2009年拍攝《哈利波特：混血王子的背叛》期間，Alan Rickman曾經寫過一篇名為「Inside Snape&rsquo;s Head」的文章，表達了他對導演David Yates不滿，內容提到導演David Yates認為「石內卜」一角對故事發展並不重要，例如對青少年欠缺吸引力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/220140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F220140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=70e058ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/220202_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F220202_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5bff7d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/220210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F220210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f198de72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n石內卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6428df950c559cc4d756b434c575200867cc0486","tid":776985,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f2e095a304d17dc3c6f1e337a777e4dd5df207","tid":776985,"